{"tid":1608166,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉載][借AC]被捕人士資訊","createTime":"2019-10-01T08:19:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T06:45:12.000Z","uid":87216,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"713bf63b29760e99df3be4deadbf674bc0afffd1","tid":1608166,"uid":87216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:19:34.000Z","msg":"⚠️被捕人士資訊⚠️<br />\n<br />\n你絕對有權保持沉默 千祈唔好答唔知道<br />\n真係忍唔住出聲就答 我唔答 或者 我無嘢講<br />\n<br />\n你可以要求打電話比屋企人朋友同埋律師<br />\n無律師在場盡量唔好簽任何文件<br />\n<br />\n最好都係搵律師陪你 你可以搵相熟或者義務律師 千祈唔好怕麻煩<br />\n如果唔係你有機會比扣留48個鐘 到時你嘅精神好難保持喺非常清醒嘅狀態去應付成個扣留過程<br />\n<br />\n盡量記低比扣查嘅過程 包括時間 人物 地點 以供日後有需要嘅時候參考返<br />\n<br />\n如果有需要簽保釋 你需要準備一筆現金 一般人都唔會有咁多錢喺身 所以記得要準備聯絡到隨時可以幫你比保釋金(/律師費)嘅人<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家幫手補充 不用like 歡迎share<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B3ERDchB8XE/?igshid=3o3m6dst613a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3ERDchB8XE%2F%3Figshid%3D3o3m6dst613a&d=6oYmF1jQM6ZNNDbF9UcscTw60zqfRdeCYg0zJNkavsY%3D&h=2f6c2b1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB3ERDchB8XE%2F%3Figshid%3D3o3m6dst613a&h=d43df4a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B3ERDchB8XE/?igshid=3o3m6dst613a</a>"},{"pid":"8195eff022ef7700b27b02cc7e944595cabc1f91","tid":1608166,"uid":87216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba968882a0a1554476cd948cc91ae48a5cb82226","tid":1608166,"uid":87216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T08:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" cl